{"tid":2058353,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"女生過夜「我覺得妳沒有不要」印度男被控性侵：感覺她身體很刺激","createTime":"2020-06-10T06:00:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T09:30:32.000Z","uid":32511,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b5995ada3d6a255f546c9713cc54689292134a85","tid":2058353,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T06:00:02.000Z","msg":"20多歲印度籍男子與一30多歲女子相約在住處喝酒、聊天，女子不勝疲勞睡著，印度男卻從背後靠近，撫摸女子胸部，用手侵入下體性侵得逞，女子氣得立刻上警局報案。印度男辯稱，以為女子在他家過夜，睡覺的時候還碰到他就是在「暗示」，且過程中女子的身體反應感覺很「Exciting」，也沒有拒絕。不過檢方認為，印度男根本沒看到女子的臉，女子也有說「不要」，因此將印度男依強制性交罪起訴。<br />\n <br />\n檢方追查，女子和印度男透過網路認識，事發前2人相約見面喝酒、聊天，卻因喬不攏地點，最後決定在印度男的租屋套房內。赴約前，女子因宿疾先到醫院回診，拿了醫生開的處方藥，與印度男聊天時配水服用。只是似乎藥物含有安眠、肌肉鬆弛成分，女子不勝疲累，也不想回家，便躺在印度男的床上休息。<br />\n <br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=759121\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D759121&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVa%2Fkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=4348f3c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D759121&h=1bb4e136\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=759121</a>"},{"pid":"d5a1261629860e2926c8458474209d4b59374e01","tid":2058353,"uid":138019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T06:08:37.000Z","msg":"印度版連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c0a0e09e26802d3ca49a04b9a46961c1472d942","tid":2058353,"uid":47309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T07:03:31.000Z","msg":"但係訓同一張床<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7d25e12e745c032738959d5d361e6e6bfb04544","tid":2058353,"uid":249015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T07:20:37.000Z","msg":"係人地屋企過夜都無暗示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5e2e91bef46cea4bdd2a94a829a3f37f9